name: Operational As Planned (V)
Text: 'Once per turn, if taken into hand using Protocol Failure, may immediately reveal this Interrupt to return Protocol Failure from Lost Pile to hand.  Use 1 Force to take [Virtual Block 6] Grotto Werribee or an Immediate Effect into hand from Reserve Deck; reshuffle.  OR Use 2 Force to take an Effect that deploys for free into hand from Reserve Deck; reshuffle.',
